&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Financial modelling to evaluate new investment opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Carry out market research through review of third-party research reports, analyse market trends by conducting primary research and visiting competing projects/ assets. Actively contribute to sector initiatives, become knowledge resource for sector insights and expertise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct due diligence in support of transactions under the direction of the senior investment team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare screening memos, investment committee memos for new investments and exits.&lt;/li&gt;
